codeText: public static InputStream filterToXContent(HttpRequest request, XContent xContent, ToXContent.Params params,_                                               String excludeField) throws IOException {_        try (ByteArrayOutputStream bos = new ByteArrayOutputStream()__             XContentBuilder filteredBuilder = new XContentBuilder(xContent, bos,_                     Collections.emptySet(), Collections.singleton(excludeField))) {_            request.toXContent(filteredBuilder, params)__            filteredBuilder.flush()__            return new ByteArrayInputStream(bos.toByteArray())__        }_    }
